text: Krasnodubrovsk () is a rural locality (a village) in Belsky Selsoviet, Gafuriysky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 12 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 10 km from Krasnousolsky, 7 km from Inzelga. == References == Category:Rural localities in Gafuriysky District
title: Krasnodubrovsk
